            <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/section/sports/basketball/mens">MEN&#039;S BASKETBALL</a></span></div>

                <h1>After season of &#039;learning&#039; for Duke men&#039;s basketball, it&#039;s time for the final exam</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/8cccf38c-9ace-402e-ab10-56989386e2c5.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Losing&#x20;to&#x20;North&#x20;Carolina&#x20;was&#x20;yet&#x20;another&#x20;learning&#x20;experience&#x20;in&#x20;the&#x20;eyes&#x20;of&#x20;many&#x20;Blue&#x20;Devils." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            Losing to North Carolina was yet another learning experience in the eyes of many Blue Devils.

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/ian-jaffe">Ian Jaffe</a> |
                                                                                                                                The Chronicle
                                                                            </figcaption>
                                </aside>
                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/mitchell-gladstone">Mitchell Gladstone</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">March 11, 2018 | 3:17am EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2018/03/after-season-of-learning-for-duke-mens-basketball-its-time-for-the-final-exam" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
